# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# CAFE FINDER AI — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── App ──────────────────────────────────
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your-super-secret-nextauth-key-change-this-in-production

# ─── Database ─────────────────────────────
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://<username>:<password>@cluster.mongodb.net/cafefinder?retryWrites=true&w=majority

# ─── OpenAI ───────────────────────────────
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# ─── Google Places API ────────────────────
# Enable "Places API" at: https://console.cloud.google.com
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=AIza...

# ─── Mapbox ───────────────────────────────
# Get your token at: https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.eyJ1...

# ─── Google OAuth (optional) ──────────────
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=

# ─── App Config ───────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_PLACES_KEY=AIza...
